@startuml
title Data Flow in Justice40 Tool

participant "ETL Pipeline" as ETL
participant "S3 Data Lake" as S3
participant "Scoring Module" as Scoring
participant "Map Tile Generator" as MapGen
participant "Client Application" as Client

ETL -> S3: Extract and transform data
ETL -> S3: Store processed data
S3 --> Scoring: Retrieve data for scoring
Scoring -> S3: Store calculated scores
S3 --> MapGen: Retrieve GeoJSON data
MapGen -> S3: Store generated map tiles
Client -> S3: Request map tiles and data
S3 --> Client: Serve map tiles and data
Client -> Client: Render map and display information

@enduml